social_posts.post_text: One of the best feelings in the world is being in LOVE! I love, love 💋❤️
Staying UP is a mindset of abundance taking action and living out your destiny!
Studying for Law School has made it difficult for me to find time for the little things! I promise to make time for you! Love you😘😊
I was at the gym and God told me to be prepared for the haters and lies! I don't take anything personally! I'm a SuperStar! I made it! “Let the games begin!
You gotta keep your standards high… The best respect is self respect!
What God has for you won’t miss you!! Everything will manifest on time! Keep the faith & keep going! Over 200 songs written &recorded I’m not stopping! #gametime #millionarelifestyle #goodvibes

Let's not pretend like spiritual warfare is not real. I didn't chose to be an Artist it chose me! I tried to run from it but the Music keeps calling me! Whats interesting about my music is during writing each song I was dealing with different spirits unaware at the time but through time it was revealed. For Example my song called (Not Friends ) my inner voice was warning me about an Ex friend that tried to drug me & kill me! True story!!God revealed the demon sent to attacks me and it was python spirit google it. It's a spirit that's envious /jealous aka a fake friend. Long story short. I walked through the valley of the shadow of death with this music! Avoided all kind of crazyness in Atlanta around all kinds of stuff! Yeah I got the tea! More to communicate!! In the mean time check out my Song “ Not Friends” on all streaming platforms QueenTizo 😘
You deserve the best and accept only the best! Self love, self respect & high self esteem! In 2023 we only participate is high frequency things! Having high standards is a must! #
